<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Ownership Transfer Complete - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">✅ Transfer Complete</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{oldOwnerName}},</p>

    <p>The ownership transfer for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> has been completed successfully.</p>

    <div style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Transfer Summary:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Store:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{storeName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>New Owner:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{newOwnerName}} ({{newOwnerEmail}})</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Your Previous Role:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-decoration: line-through;">Owner</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Your New Role:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #4CAF50; font-weight: bold;">Admin</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Transfer Completed:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{completedAt}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>What this means for you:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>✅ You retain Admin access to the store</li>
      <li>✅ You can still manage most store operations</li>
      <li>❌ You can no longer manage subscriptions or billing</li>
      <li>❌ You can no longer transfer ownership</li>
      <li>❌ You can no longer delete the store</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Note:</strong> If you no longer need access to this store, you can leave at any time from your account settings. The new owner can also modify your role or remove your access.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{storeUrl}}" style="background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
        View Store
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      Thank you for your contributions to {{storeName}}!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
